# Problem Description
Show your data analysis based on division ( For district wise, follow same way), Here I use javascript, You can add it in your own way. Thank me later. 

## License

Released under [Riseup Labs](/LICENSE) by [@arafat](https://bd.linkedin.com/in/arafat-rahman-b2a948174).

# Instruction

## File Description
- index.html file has overall code that show the map data using JS
- division.sql / district.sql  has basic column named map_d_path,text_transform which is responsible to make map. map_d_path is responsible for "d" attribute`s value and text_tramnsform is responsible for position of each "g" name. each "g" represents each district or division.

## Call a function to render these data to generate the map

```javascript
generateGTagForMap(division_json);


 function generateGTagForMap(division_json){

        var html = '';
        division_json.forEach((data) => {

        html +=  '<g data-id="';
        html+=data.id+' id="div_'+data.id+'"><path d="'+data.map_d+'" fill="'+data.area_bg+'" stroke="#848484" stroke-width="0.765487" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />';
        html+= '<text transform="matrix('+data.text_transform+')" class="st3">'+data.name+' </text></g>';                    
        });
        
        //render data
        $('#my-svg').html('');
        $('#my-svg').html(html);
}

# output
show a map
```

## Javascript for zoom in , zoom out, move, refresh, fullscreen

```javascript
//SVG button controller related
                var svgContainer = document.getElementById('svg-container');
                var svg = document.getElementById('my-svg');
                var zoomInBtn = document.getElementById('zoom-in-btn');
                var zoomOutBtn = document.getElementById('zoom-out-btn');
                var refreshBtn = document.getElementById('refresh-btn');
                var fullPageBtn = document.getElementById('full-page-btn');
                var currentScale = 1;
                var isDragging = false;
                var startDragX = 0;
                var startDragY = 0;
                var currentTranslateX = 0;
                var currentTranslateY = 0;
            
                zoomInBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
                  currentScale += 0.1;
                  svg.style.transform = 'scale(' + currentScale + ') translate(' + currentTranslateX + 'px, ' + currentTranslateY + 'px)';
                });
            
                zoomOutBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
                  currentScale -= 0.1;
                  svg.style.transform = 'scale(' + currentScale + ') translate(' + currentTranslateX + 'px, ' + currentTranslateY + 'px)';
                });
            
                refreshBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
                  currentScale = 1;
                  currentTranslateX = 0;
                  currentTranslateY = 0;
                  svg.style.transform = 'scale(1) translate(0, 0)';
                });
            
                fullPageBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
                  if (svgContainer.requestFullscreen) {
                    svgContainer.requestFullscreen();
                  } 
                });
            
                svgContainer.addEventListener('mousedown', startDrag);
                svgContainer.addEventListener('touchstart', startDrag);
                svgContainer.addEventListener('mousemove', drag);
                svgContainer.addEventListener('touchmove', drag);
                svgContainer.addEventListener('mouseup', endDrag);
                svgContainer.addEventListener('touchend', endDrag);
            
                function startDrag(event) {
                  event.preventDefault();
                  isDragging = true;
                  if (event.type === 'mousedown') {
                    startDragX = event.clientX;
                    startDragY = event.clientY;
                  } else if (event.type === 'touchstart') {
                    startDragX = event.touches[0].clientX;
                    startDragY = event.touches[0].clientY;
                  }
                }
            
                function drag(event) {
                  event.preventDefault();
                  if (!isDragging) return;
                  var currentX = 0;
                  var currentY = 0;
                  if (event.type === 'mousemove') {
                    currentX = event.clientX;
                    currentY = event.clientY;
                  } else if (event.type === 'touchmove') {
                    currentX = event.touches[0].clientX;
                    currentY = event.touches[0].clientY;
                  }
                  var deltaX = currentX - startDragX;
                  var deltaY = currentY - startDragY;
                  currentTranslateX += deltaX;
                  currentTranslateY += deltaY;
                  svg.style.transform = 'scale(' + currentScale + ') translate(' + currentTranslateX + 'px, ' + currentTranslateY + 'px)';
                  startDragX = currentX;
                  startDragY = currentY;
                }
            
                function endDrag(event) {
                  event.preventDefault();
                  isDragging = false;
                }
```
